Steps to create First Rsp Hrs By Days of the week Chart 12

       i.         Drag and drop First Rsp Hrs on the row field.

        ii.        Right click on SUM (First Rsp Hrs)

        iii.       Then right click on Measure (SUM)

        iv.        Then click Average

         v.       Drag and drop Created on the column shelves.

        vi.       Right click on Year(created).

        vii.       Click on More then select weekday.

        viii.       Click on marks card drop down arrow.

        ix.       Then select Bar chart.

x.     Format the the color of the Bars

        a.    Click on Color Card and click More Colors

        b.    Replace the values Red: 62, Green: 148, and Blue: 172

        c.     Click OK
